{"type": "article", "id": 12176, "title": "J.Crew x New Balance 合作鞋款", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-16T10:29:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135117SRBgfYxcIPNr6Qs7.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最近，文艺少女最喜欢的品牌 J.Crew 和 New Balance 合作了，他们一起推出了一款 Neptune Blue 全新配色鞋子，鞋子脱胎于 New Balance 经典跑鞋 996，选用了深蓝搭配灰色，看上去干净时尚，同时，天蓝色的 Logo 嵌入黑色麂皮中，后跟的一抹天蓝色也让鞋子看起来更加活泼。鞋子今日登陆J.Crew 门店，并将于 21 日登陆线上，<a href=\"https://www.jcrew.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140015eWJ7St9iH6qEgvoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140015Pn0IClHJX5vmGegB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}